to start the datacollection on several computers use the following command:

open terminal on kullback:
go to berkeley_sawyer/launch/bridgeonly
run ./startkinect_kullback.sh

if you want to do random movements:
run rosrun berkeley_sawyer primitives.py

if you just want to save images
run rosrun berkeley_sawyer test_recorder.py

open terminal on kinectbox1:
go to launch/bridgeonly
run ./startkinect_kinect1.sh
run rosrun berkeley_saweyer robot_recorder.py